commit.message: Raise qt version to LTS 5.15.2
Fix readme and cmake config

Fix building the tests with Qt 6 (#332)

* Remove usage of QTEST_ADD_GPU_BLACKLIST_SUPPORT_DEFS

According to commit 641eb4a96552615d898512723e2093abcaf7fbc1 in
qtbase.git they serve no purpose anymore and were subsequently removed
in Qt6.

Closes #331.

* Replace QLatin1Literal with QStringLiteral

The former is deprecated and was removed from Qt6.

commit.message:
Allow building against Qt6 (#327)

* Use C++17

This is required for Qt6 support

* Port away from deprecated QPalette::background

* Port away from deprecated qSort

* Port away from deprecated QString::SplitBehavior

* Port away from deprecated QLineF::intersect

* Port away from deprecated QDesktopWidget

* Port away from deprecated Qt::MidButton

* Port away from deprecated QGraphicsView::resetMatrix

* Port away from deprecated QEvent::pos

* Fix duplicate shortcut in action tooltip

Qt already adds the action to the tooltip, adding it ourself causes duplication

* Port away from deprecated QFontMetrics::width

* Adjust build system to support Qt6
